---
title: Crumbed Haloumi Caesar-Style Salad with Croutons & Creamy Dressing
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful crumbed haloumi meets a
caesar-style salad tossed in a tangy and creamy dressing, then topped with sharp Parmesan to finish it off.
